headline: NetApp: Fiscal Q4 Earnings Snapshot
summary: The average estimate of nine analysts surveyed by Zacks Investment Research was for earnings of $1.90 per share. The data storage company posted revenue of $1.73 billion in the period, matching Street forecasts. For the year, the company reported profit of $1.19 billion, or $5.67 per share.

headline: NetApp’s (NASDAQ:NTAP) Q1 Sales Beat Estimates But Full-Year Sales Guidance Slightly Misses Expectations
summary: Data storage company NetApp (NASDAQ:NTAP) reported Q1 CY2025 results topping the market’s revenue expectations, with sales up 3.8% year on year to $1.73 billion. On the other hand, next quarter’s revenue guidance of $1.53 billion was less impressive, coming in 4.5% below analysts’ estimates. Its non-GAAP profit of $1.93 per share was 1.8% above analysts’ consensus estimates.
